# AccessMate user data (never commit personal settings).
# Real user data lives in %APPDATA%/AccessMate/ (outside the repo) and can
# never be committed. These patterns additionally guard against accidental
# local runtime data if the app is ever run from inside the project folder.
/app.json
*.log

